	<h1 class="title">「日本語」中国游客“爆买”健在，只是换了一波购买对象</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/147/small/147.jpg?1418116339" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陈思吟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-13 11:26:44 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22171/medium/22171.jpg?1455326454" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22171" data-title="《「日本語」中国游客“爆买”健在，只是换了一波购买对象》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22171/medium/22171.jpg?1455326454" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22171.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
